review_blob: Excellent beer. It is not my favorite, or even close. It is just a good beer to sit down and drink with some friends. You dont covert this beer, you just drink it. You enjoy it. Not quite a session beer, but its good for any occasion.
As soon as it hits the mouth, the taste is slightly off-putting but is quickly muted and there is little/no aftertaste. Refreshing, although the alcohol is clearly not hidden.
